isDisableDispNum01.Wiki:
These flags determine what item type the material is.
00000/00001: Weapon
10000/10001: Armor
01000/01001: Accessory
00100/00101: Goods
00010/00011: Gem (Unused)
11110: Ignore Requirement

pad1.Wiki:
First 4 bytes are also Item Type flags. Values are as follows:
0/16: Weapon
1/17: Armor
2/18: Accessory
4/20: Goods
8/24: Gem (Unused)
15: Ignore Requirement
